\c 11
\s Atariya mai vaAhaziya anobata ushe hwaJudha
\p
\v 1 Atariya mai vaAhaziya\x + 8.26. Vato. 9.5.\x* paakaona kuti mwanakomana wake wafa, wakasimuka ndokuparadza mbeu yose yeumambo\x + 2 Makor. 22.10. 24.1.\x*.
\v 2 Asi Jehoshebha mukunda wamambo Joramu, hanzvadzi yaAhaziya, wakatora Joashi mwanakomana waAhaziya, ndokumuba kubva pakati pevanakomana vamambo vaiurawa, iye nemureri wake mukamuri yemibhedha. Zvino vakamuviga pachiso chaAtariya kuti asaurawa.
\v 3 Zvino waiva naye muimba yaJehovha akazvivanza makore matanhatu; Atariya ndokutonga pamusoro penyika.
\p
\v 4 Zvino negore rechinomwe Jehoyadha wakatuma \add nhume \add*ndokutora misoro yemazana\x + 11.9. 2 Makor. 22.11.\x* yevaKari\x + 11.19. 2 Sam. 20.23.\x* neyevarindi\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*, ndokuiunza kwaari muimba yaJehovha, ndokuita sungano navo, ndokuvapikisa muimba yaJehovha, ndokuvaratidza mwanakomana wamambo.
\v 5 Zvino wakavaraira achiti: Ichi chinhu chamuchaita: Chetatu chenyu chinopinda nesabata chichava varindi vechirindo cheimba yamambo\x + 1 Makor. 9.25.\x*;
\v 6 uye chetatu chichava pasuwo reSuri\x + 2 Makor. 23.5.\x*; uye chetatu pasuwo shure kwevarindi\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*; saizvozvo muchachengeta chirindo cheimba, isapaziwa.
\v 7 Zvino mapoka maviri enyu mese munobuda nesabata, naivo vachachengetedza chirindo cheimba yaJehovha maererano namambo\x + 1 Makor. 9.25.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino muchakomba mambo kupoteredza, murume umwe neumwe ane zvombo zvake muruoko rwake\x + 6.14.\x*; uye anopinda pamisara achaurawa\x + 11.15. 1 Madz. 6.9.\x*. Muve namambo pakubuda kwake nepakupinda kwake\x + Num.. 27.17.\x*.
\v 9 Zvino misoro yemazana yakaita zvinoenderana nezvose mupristi Jehoyadha zvaakaraira; ndokutora umwe neumwe vanhu vake vaipinda nesabata, pamwe nevaibuda nesabata, ndokusvika kuna Jehoyadha mupristi\x + 1 Makor. 9.25.\x*.
\v 10 Zvino mupristi wakapa misoro yemazana mapfumo nenhovo zvaiva zvamambo Dhavhidhi zvaiva mumba maJehovha\x + 1 Makor. 18.7. 2 Sam. 8.7.\x*.
\v 11 Zvino varindi vakamira, umwe neumwe ane zvombo zvake muruoko rwake, kubva kudivi rerudyi reimba kusvika kudivi reruboshwe reimba, paaritari nepaimba kuna mambo mativi ese\x + 10.25. 1 Sam. 22.17.\x*.
\v 12 Zvino wakabudisa mwanakomana wamambo, ndokuisa korona pamusoro pake\x + 2 Sam. 1.10.\x*, nechipupuriro, zvino vakamuisa akava mambo, vakamuzodza; ndokurova maoko, ndokuti: Mambo ngaararame\x + Eki. 25.16. 31.18. Det. 17.18.\x*!
\p
\v 13 Atariya paakanzwa mhere-mhere yevarindi \add ne\add*vanhu, wakaenda kuvanhu muimba yaJehovha.
\v 14 Zvino wakaona, tarira zvino, mambo amire pambiru setsika, nevatungamiriri nevaridzi vehwamanda vari kuna mambo\x + 23.3. 2 Makor. 34.31.\x*; uye vanhu vose venyika vakafara vachiridza dzihwamanda\x + 1 Madz. 1.34.\x*. Zvino Atariya akabvarura nguvo dzake, ndokudanidzira achiti: Kurongera, kurongera\x + Gen.. 44.13.\x*!
\v 15 Zvino Jehoyadha mupristi wakaraira misoro yemazana, vabati vehondo\x + Num.. 31.14. 2 Makor. 23.14.\x*, ndokuti kwavari: Mubudisirei kunze kwemisara\x + 11.15. 1 Madz. 6.9.\x*; neanomutevera mumuuraye nemunondo. Nokuti mupristi wakati: Ngaasaurairwa muimba yaJehovha.
\v 16 Zvino vakamubata nemaoko, iye ndokuenda nenzira mabhiza yaakapinda nayo muimba yamambo, ndokuurayirwapo\x + 2 Makor. 23.15.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Zvino Jehoyadha wakaita sungano pakati paJehovha namambo nevanhu, kuti vave vanhu vaJehovha\x + Josh. 24.25.\x*; uye pakati pamambo nevanhu\x + 2 Sam. 5.3.\x*.
\v 18 Zvino vanhu vose venyika vakapinda muimba yaBhaari, ndokuiputsira pasi\x + 10.21,26.\x*; aritari dzake nemifananidzo yake vakazviparadza kwazvo, uye Matani mupristi waBhaari vakamuuraya pamberi pedziaritari\x + Det. 12.3.\x*. Mupristi ndokuisa vatariri pamusoro peimba yaJehovha.
\v 19 Zvino wakatora misoro yemazana, nevaKari, nevarindi, nevanhu vose venyika, ndokuburusa mambo kubva paimba yaJehovha\x + 11.4.\x*, ndokuuya nenzira yesuwo revarindi kuimba yamambo. Zvino akagara pachigaro cheushe chemadzimambo\x + 11.6. 2 Makor. 23.20.\x*.
\v 20 Zvino vanhu vose venyika vakafara, guta ndokuva murunyararo, vauraya Atariya nemunondo \add pa\add*imba yamambo.
\v 21 Jehoashi waiva ane makore manomwe paakava mambo.